OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775289887
OL,3,CTrump mocks Starmer as weak as UK
OL,4,Cleads push to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FDonald Trump has mocked Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer as weak and had a fresh dig at
OL,8,Fthe UK's navy as Britain led
OL,9,Fdiplomatic efforts to try and reopen
OL,10,Fthe critical Strait of Hormuz shipping
OL,11,Flane, closed by the Iran war.
OL,13,FThe US president impersonated the
OL,14,FPrime Minister as he recounted Sir
OL,15,FKeir saying he had to ask his team
OL,16,Fabout sending "two old broken-down
OL,17,Faircraft carriers" to the Middle East.
OL,26,@xD@OOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
