PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775289887
OL,3,CTrump mocks Starmer as weak as UK
OL,4,Cleads push to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FMr Trump said Britain "should be our
OL,7,Fbest" ally, but had not been in his
OL,8,Flatest sideswipe over the UK's refusal
OL,9,Fto be drawn into the conflict with
OL,10,FTehran, which has emerged in a video
OL,11,Ffrom a private Easter White House
OL,12,Flunch.
OL,14,FIt is not the first time the American
OL,15,Fleader has been critical of the UK's
OL,16,Faircraft carriers, having previously
OL,17,Fdismissed them as "toys" that "aren't
OL,18,Fthe best".
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@EO]yD@SOUyD@XO]yD@_OUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
