PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775289887
OL,3,CTrump mocks Starmer as weak as UK
OL,4,Cleads push to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FEarlier this week, US defence
OL,7,Fsecretary Pete Hegseth rounded on
OL,8,FBritain for failing to send warships
OL,9,Fto the region, saying "last time I
OL,10,Fchecked there was supposed to be a
OL,11,Fbig, bad Royal Navy that could be
OL,12,Fprepared to do things like that as
OL,13,Fwell".
OL,15,FTheir disparaging remarks come as the
OL,16,FKing, who is head of the armed forces,
OL,17,Fis due to travel to Washington later
OL,18,Fthis month for a state visit to mark
OL,19,Fthe 250th anniversary of American
OL,20,Findependence.
OL,26,@qD@WOUuD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
