PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775289887
OL,3,CTrump mocks Starmer as weak as UK
OL,4,Cleads push to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FSpeaking at the lunch on Wednesday, Mr
OL,7,FTrump said: "I asked (the) UK, who
OL,8,Fshould be our best.
OL,10,F"In fact the King is coming over here
OL,11,Fin two weeks, he's a nice guy, King
OL,12,FCharles.
OL,14,F"But should be our best but they
OL,15,Fweren't our best.
OL,17,F"I said 'you have two, old broken-down
OL,18,Faircraft carriers, do you think you
OL,19,Fcould send them over'?"
OL,26,@oD@MOUrD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
