OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775289887
OL,3,CTrump mocks Starmer as weak as UK
OL,4,Cleads push to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FImpersonating Sir Keir with a weak
OL,7,Fvoice, Mr Trump added: "Ohhh I'll have
OL,8,Fto ask my team.
OL,10,F"I said 'you're the Prime Minister,
OL,11,Fyou don't have to'.
OL,13,F"No, no, no, I have to ask my team. My
OL,14,Fteam has to meet, we're meeting next
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,F"But the war already started. Next
OL,18,Fweek the war's going to be over... in
OL,19,Fthree days."
OL,26,@oD@XOUrD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU{D@LO]
