PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775289887
OL,3,CTrump mocks Starmer as weak as UK
OL,4,Cleads push to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,F"Iran's closure of the Strait of
OL,7,FHormuz is a direct threat to global
OL,8,Fprosperity," she said in a statement
OL,9,Ffollowing the virtual meeting on
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,12,F"Iran is trying to hold the global
OL,13,Feconomy hostage in the Strait of
OL,14,FHormuz.
OL,16,F"They must not prevail. To that
OL,17,Feffect, partners today called for the
OL,18,Fimmediate and unconditional reopening
OL,19,Fof the Strait and respect for the
OL,20,Ffundamental principles of freedom of
OL,21,Fnavigation and the law of the sea."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]tD@AOUxD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
