OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775289887
OL,3,CTrump mocks Starmer as weak as UK
OL,4,Cleads push to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FBritain is seeking to lead the
OL,7,Fdiplomatic initiative, including
OL,8,Fcountries such as France, Germany and
OL,9,Fsome Gulf nations, after Mr Trump
OL,10,Fsignalled it was up to others to
OL,11,Funblock the waterway not relied upon
OL,12,Fby the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
