PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775289887
OL,3,CTrump mocks Starmer as weak as UK
OL,4,Cleads push to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FAfter chairing the video call, Ms
OL,7,FCooper told broadcasters on Thursday:
OL,8,F"We've taken a different view from the
OL,9,FUS from early on and we didn't get
OL,10,Fdrawn into offensive action in the
OL,11,FMiddle East, because we thought that
OL,12,Fthere were real concerns about
OL,13,Fescalation risks, impact ` including
OL,14,Fon the economy ` and also the need for
OL,15,Fa proper plan."
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
