FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775289887
OL,3,CTrump mocks Starmer as weak as UK
OL,4,Cleads push to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FMs Cooper ducked a question on whether
OL,7,FWashington was still an ally, saying:
OL,8,F"We want to see the conflict resolved,
OL,9,Fconcluded, as rapidly as possible,
OL,10,Fbecause, frankly, that's what's best
OL,11,Ffor the cost of living here in the UK."
OL,13,FAnother meeting next Tuesday of
OL,14,Fmilitary planners will consider how to
OL,15,F"keep shipping safe for the long-
OL,16,Fterm", Ms Cooper said, including
OL,17,Flooking at issues such as clearing
OL,18,Fmines that have possibly been laid by
OL,19,FTehran to sink ships in the sea
OL,20,Fpassage.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@gO]wD@AOUxD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
