PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1775289887
OL,3,CTrump mocks Starmer as weak as UK
OL,4,Cleads push to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FMr Trump, in an address to the US
OL,7,Fpeople on Wednesday, said countries
OL,8,Fthat rely on the strait should "build
OL,9,Fup some delayed courage" and "just
OL,10,Fgrab it", and suggested that after the
OL,11,FIran conflict was over, the critical
OL,12,Fwaterway would "just open up
OL,13,Fnaturally".
OL,15,FBut Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,16,Fhas said that unblocking the lane will
OL,17,F"not be easy".
